</taxonomicName>
(Linnaeus, 1758) (
<bibRefCitation id="FB1322CC3ACBE484C4C68E91B2445DAB" author="Shaw, SR" journalOrPublisher="Journal of Hymenoptera Research" pageId="0" pageNumber="105" pagination="131 - 137" refId="B21" refString="Shaw, SR, Salerno, G, Colazza, S, Peri, E, 2001. First record of Aridelus rufotestaceus Tobias (Hymenoptera: Braconidae, Euphorinae) parasitizing Nezara viridula nymphs (Heteroptera: Pentatomidae) with observations on its immature stages and development. Journal of Hymenoptera Research 10: 131 - 137" title="First record of Aridelus rufotestaceus Tobias (Hymenoptera: Braconidae, Euphorinae) parasitizing Nezara viridula nymphs (Heteroptera: Pentatomidae) with observations on its immature stages and development." volume="10" year="2001">Shaw et al. 2001</bibRefCitation>
